text: Jönköpings-Posten (JP) is a newspaper in Sweden. It is based in the town of Jönköping. It was started on 17 January 1865. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1865 establishments in Europe Category:Newspapers published in Sweden Category:Jönköping Category:19th- century establishments in Sweden
